Building Photon:
  use cmake to generate build files.
  run make or open project file depending on the generator used.

  project has been built successfully using clang & gcc on Linux, and mingw & msvc12 on Windows.

libraries:
  Freetype2 (freetype.org)
  GLEW (glew.sourceforge.net)
  GLM (glm.g-truc.net)
  LibXML2 (xmlsoft.org)
  Lua (5.2 lua.org)
  OpenGL (2 or later)
  PhysFS (2 or later, icculus.org/physfs/)
  SDL2 (libsdl.org)
